===2020 census===
As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], there were 29 people, 4 households, and 4 families residing in the city.<ref name="Census2020DP">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic Profile (DP1)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dp?get=NAME,DP1_0021P,DP1_0024P,DP1_0025C,DP1_0049C,DP1_0045C,DP1_0069C,DP1_0073C,DP1_0125P,DP1_0126P,DP1_0129P,DP1_0133P,DP1_0137P,DP1_0138P,DP1_0139P,DP1_0141P,DP1_0142P,DP1_0143P,DP1_0145P,DP1_0146P,DP1_0147C,DP1_0148C,DP1_0149C,DP1_0156C,DP1_0157C,DP1_0158C,DP1_0159P,DP1_0160P&for=place%3A24825&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref><ref name="Census2020PL">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Redistricting Data (Public Law 94-171)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/pl?get=NAME,P1_001N,P1_003N,P1_004N,P1_005N,P1_006N,P1_007N,P1_008N,P1_009N,P2_001N,P2_002N,H1_001N,H1_002N&for=place%3A24825&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref> The [[population density]] was 116.7 inhabitants per square mile (45.0/km<sup>2</sup>). There were 12 housing units at an average density of 48.3 per square mile (18.6/km<sup>2</sup>).<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

The median age in the city was 45.8 years. 34.5% of residents were under the age of 18. 34.5% of the residents were under the age of 20; 0.0% were between the ages of 20 and 24; 10.3% were from 25 to 44; 44.8% were from 45 to 64; and 10.3% were 65 years of age or older. For every 100 females there were 70.6 males, and for every 100 females age 18 and over there were 90.0 males age 18 and over. The gender makeup of the city was 41.4% male and 58.6% female.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

All residents lived in rural areas.<ref name="Census2020DHC">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic and Housing Characteristics (DHC)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dhc?get=NAME,P2_002N,P2_003N&for=place%3A24825&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2023|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref>

Of the 4 households, 25.0% had children under the age of 18 living in them. Of all households, 100.0% were married-couple households, 0.0% were cohabitating couples, 0.0% were households with a male householder and no spouse or partner present, and 0.0% were households with a female householder and no spouse or partner present. 0.0% of all households were non-families. 0.0% of all households were made up of individuals, and 0.0% had someone living alone who was 65 years of age or older.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

There were 12 housing units, of which 66.7% were vacant. The homeowner vacancy rate was 20.0% and the rental vacancy rate was 50.0%.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

